  "text": "Numerous tools with potential application to dietary assessment in clinical settings have been 75 reported [CITATION_1] . All these tools do not report the same dietary information (fat intake, with or 76 without other nutrients, adherence to the Mediterranean diet, or fruit and vegetable intake). 77",
